stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> Composed: createConfigurationPlatform(deps)
  Composed --> Loading: init()

  Loading --> Validating: providers loaded + precedence resolved
  Validating --> Active: schema valid (version = 1)
  Validating --> InitFailed: invalid initial config
  InitFailed --> [*]: init() throws (cannot activate)

  Active --> Reloading: reload() / provider push / setOverride
  Reloading --> Diffing: providers loaded + resolved + validated
  Diffing --> Active: no change (version stable)
  Diffing --> Changed: keys changed (version + 1)
  Changed --> Active: cache set · watchers notified · events published

  Reloading --> RollingBack: new config invalid
  RollingBack --> Active: keep previous snapshot\nValidationFailed + Rollback events

  Active --> Disposed: dispose()
  Disposed --> [*]
